      <section class="hero contact-hero" style="--hero-image: url('images/child-getting-education-home.webp')"><div class="hero-inner"><div class="hero-copy"><p class="eyebrow">Contact</p><h1>Get in touch with<br class="mobile-break" /> our team</h1><p>Whether you are making a referral, asking about a child in our care, applying for a role or looking for general information, we are here and happy to talk.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="button" href="#contact-form">Send a Message</a><a class="button secondary" href="tel:+441184400118">Call 0118 440 0118</a></div></div></div></section>
      <section class="section contact-grid">
        <aside class="contact-panel"><p class="section-label">Direct contact</p><h2>How to reach us</h2><p><span class="phone-large">0118 440 0118</span></p><p><strong>Email:</strong><br /><a href="mailto:info@animatecare.co.uk">info@animatecare.co.uk</a></p><p><strong>Careers:</strong><br /><a href="mailto:careers@animatecare.co.uk">careers@animatecare.co.uk</a></p><p><strong>Registered office:</strong><br />Suite W02, Howard Road, Stanmore, England, HA7 1FW</p></aside>
        <form class="contact-panel contact-form" id="contact-form" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" data-contact-form>
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="YOUR_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY" />
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New Animate Care website enquiry" />
          <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="Animate Care Website" />
          <h2>Send us a message</h2>
          <div class="field"><label for="name">Name</label><input id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="role">Organisation or role</label><input id="role" name="role" autocomplete="organization" /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="reason">Reason for contact</label><select id="reason" name="reason" required><option value="">Select a reason</option><option>Referral</option><option>Family enquiry</option><option>Careers</option><option>General enquiry</option></select></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="phone">Phone</label><input id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="email">Email</label><input id="email" type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="message">Message</label><textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea></div>
          <label class="consent"><input type="checkbox" required /><span>I consent to Animate Care contacting me about this enquiry. For urgent safeguarding or referral matters, I will call directly.</span></label>
          <button class="button" type="submit">Submit enquiry</button>
          <p class="form-status" data-form-status aria-live="polite"></p>
        </form>
      </section>
      <section class="band"><div class="section"><p class="section-label">Reason for contact</p><h2>What can we help you with?</h2><div class="grid four"><article class="feature"><h3>Making a Referral</h3><p>Local authority professionals should call directly for urgent enquiries and email documents for review.</p></article><article class="feature"><h3>Families</h3><p>If your child is in our care or you have questions about placement, call us at any time.</p></article><article class="feature"><h3>Careers</h3><p>Send your CV and a short note about your interest in therapeutic residential childcare.</p></article><article class="feature"><h3>General Enquiries</h3><p>For services, media or professional questions, email or call and we will direct you.</p></article></div></div></section>
      <section class="section"><p class="section-label">Transparency</p><h2>Complaints and safeguarding contacts</h2><p class="section-intro">We respond to concerns openly and promptly. If you have a concern about a child in our care, contact us directly in the first instance. Children and representatives can also contact external agencies.</p><div class="grid two"><article class="feature"><h3>Ofsted</h3><p>0300 123 1231<br /><a href="mailto:enquiries@ofsted.gov.uk">enquiries@ofsted.gov.uk</a><br />Clive House, 70 Petty France, London SW1H 9EX</p></article><article class="feature"><h3>Child Protection Support</h3><p>NSPCC: 0808 800 5000<br />Childline: 0800 1111<br />Children's Commissioner: 020 7783 8330</p></article></div></section>
      <section class="section"><h2>Contact: questions answered</h2><div class="faq-list"><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do I contact Animate Care?</summary><p>Call 0118 440 0118 or email info@animatecare.co.uk.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do I make a complaint about Animate Care?</summary><p>Contact the home directly in the first instance. Formal complaints receive a full response within 28 days. You may also contact Ofsted on 0300 123 1231.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I visit the Animate Care home before a placement?</summary><p>Yes. We encourage home visits from social workers, families, CAMHS workers and relevant professionals before a placement is confirmed.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Where is Animate Care located?</summary><p>The residential home is in the Wokingham Road area. The registered office is Suite W02, Howard Road, Stanmore, England, HA7 1FW.</p></details></div></section>
